t\";s:715:\"<p>The International Orange Blossom Carnival brings thousands of visitors from all over Turkey and the world to Adana every year. This event, held within the scope of the Ministry of Culture and Tourism\'s \'Turkey Culture Route Festivals,\' offers participants not only entertainment but also an opportunity to explore the rich historical and tourist sites in Adana and its surroundings. During the carnival, guests can closely observe the iconic structures and natural beauties of Çukurova, from the Adana Museum to Anavarza Castle, from Ashab-ı Kehf to the Atatürk House Museum, and Belemedik Plateau. This special region, where history, culture, and nature intertwine, offers visitors unforgettable moments.</p>\";s:8:\"location\";N;s:5:\"video\";N;s:15:\"youtubeplaylist\";N;s:3:\"ses\";N;s:7:\"spotify\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:4:\"icon\";s:27:\"adana-cevresi-icon-iinx.svg\";s:4:\"file\";N;s:7:\"is_main\";i:0;s:8:\"blade_id\";i:22;s:11:\"category_id\";i:8;s:14:\"translation_of\";i:91;s:11:\"parent_page\";N;s:7:\"lang_id\";i:2;s:11:\"form_active\";i:0;s:9:\"published\";i:1;s:9:\"show_menu\";i:0;s:13:\"show_homepage\";i:0;s:11:\"show_footer\";i:0;s:15:\"show_sponsorluk\";i:0;s:10:\"created_at\";s:19:\"2026-04-30 10:43:16\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:19:\"2026-04-30 10:43:16\";s:10:\"deleted_at\";N;}s:11:\"\0*\0original\";a:34:{s:2:\"id\";i:227;s:3:\"hit\";N;s:8:\"sezon_id\";N;s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"Around Adana\";s:12:\"inside_title\";N;s:4:\"slug\";s:12:\"around-adana\";s:4:\"link\";N;s:5:\"link2\";N;s:5:\"link3\";N;s:6:\"heyzen\";N;s:7:\"content\";s:715:\"<p>The International Orange Blossom Carnival brings thousands of visitors from all over Turkey and the world to Adana every year. This event, held within the scope of the Ministry of Culture and Tourism\'s \'Turkey Culture Route Festivals,\' offers participants not only entertainment but also an opportunity to explore the rich historical and tourist sites in Adana and its surroundings. During the carnival, guests can closely observe the iconic structures and natural beauties of Çukurova, from the Adana Museum to Anavarza Castle, from Ashab-ı Kehf to the Atatürk House Museum, and Belemedik Plateau. This special region, where history, culture, and nature intertwine, offers visitors unforgettable moments.</p>\";s:8:\"location\";N;s:5:\"video\";N;s:15:\"youtubeplaylist\";N;s:3:\"ses\";N;s:7:\"spotify\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:4:\"icon\";s:27:\"adana-cevresi-icon-iinx.svg\";s:4:\"file\";N;s:7:\"is_main\";i:0;s:8:\"blade_id\";i:22;s:11:\"category_id\";i:8;s:14:\"translation_of\";i:91;s:11:\"parent_page\";N;s:7:\"lang_id\";i:2;s:11:\"form_active\";i:0;s:9:\"published\";i:1;s:9:\"show_menu\";i:0;s:13:\"show_homepage\";i:0;s:11:\"show_footer\";i:0;s:15:\"show_sponsorluk\";i:0;s:10:\"created_at\";s:19:\"2026-04-30 10:43:16\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:19:\"2026-04-30 10:43:16\";s:10:\"deleted_at\";N;}s:10:\"\0*\0changes\";a:0:{}s:11:\"\0*\0previous\";a:0:{}s:8:\"\0*\0casts\";a:1:{s:10:\"deleted_at\";s:8:\"datetime\";}s:17:\"\0*\0classCastCache\";a:0:{}s:21:\"\0*\0attributeCastCache\";a:0:{}s:13:\"\0*\0dateFormat\";N;s:10:\"\0*\0appends\";a:0:{}s:19:\"\0*\0dispatchesEvents\";a:0:{}s:14:\"\0*\0observables\";a:0:{}s:12:\"\0*\0relations\";a:0:{}s:10:\"\0*\0touches\";a:0:{}s:27:\"\0*\0relationAutoloadCallback\";N;s:26:\"\0*\0relationAutoloadContext\";N;s:10:\"timestamps\";b:1;s:13:\"usesUniqueIds\";b:0;s:9:\"\0*\0hidden\";a:0:{}s:10:\"\0*\0visible\";a:0:{}s:11:\"\0*\0fillable\";a:29:{i:0;s:3:\"hit\";i:1;s:8:\"sezon_id\";i:2;s:5:\"title\";i:3;s:12:\"inside_title\";i:4;s:4:\"slug\";i:5;s:4:\"link\";i:6;s:5:\"link2\";i:7;s:5:\"link3\";i:8;s:6:\"heyzen\";i:9;s:7:\"content\";i:10;s:8:\"location\";i:11;s:5:\"video\";i:12;s:3:\"ses\";i:13;s:7:\"spotify\";i:14;s:5:\"image\";i:15;s:4:\"icon\";i:16;s:4:\"file\";i:17;s:7:\"is_main\";i:18;s:8:\"blade_id\";i:19;s:11:\"category_id\";i:20;s:14:\"translation_of\";i:21;s:11:\"parent_page\";i:22;s:7:\"lang_id\";i:23;s:11:\"form_active\";i:24;s:9:\"published\";i:25;s:13:\"