ring\";b:0;s:13:\"\0*\0attributes\";a:34:{s:2:\"id\";i:262;s:3:\"hit\";N;s:8:\"sezon_id\";N;s:5:\"title\";s:51:\"The excitement is even greater in Adana this April!\";s:12:\"inside_title\";N;s:4:\"slug\";s:50:\"the-excitement-is-even-greater-in-adana-this-april\";s:4:\"link\";N;s:5:\"link2\";N;s:5:\"link3\";N;s:6:\"heyzen\";N;s:7:\"content\";s:2517:\"<p>The International Orange Blossom Carnival promises an unforgettable surprise for its visitors in 2026. HobbyPort Mediterranean Fair is included in the Carnival program as an associated event.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe energy of the Carnival transforms into a lifestyle festival with the HobbyPort Mediterranean Fair. Taking place in Adana from April 2-5, 2026, the HobbyPort Mediterranean Fair offers visitors the opportunity to discover their dream outdoor lifestyle and the latest hobby trends.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhile the Carnival represents fun, the streets, and togetherness, HobbyPort Mediterranean transforms this energy into personal passions and a desire to return to nature. The Carnival and HobbyPort create a synergy built on the philosophy of \"living life to the fullest.\" Visitors who will experience the carnival excitement in Adana amidst the scent of orange blossoms will also have the opportunity to discover their dream outdoor lifestyle and the latest hobby trends at the fairgrounds.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Why should Carnival visitors explore HobbyPort Mediterranean?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Complete Your Carnival Experience: Let the excitement of the streets continue with a passion for adventure! Crown the free spirit of the carnival with caravans, motorcycles, and outdoor equipment that will allow you to escape into nature.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDiscover the World of Hobbies: Not just for professionals; a wide range of inspiring content awaits visitors of all ages who want to make a fresh start, including caravans, tiny houses, hunting &amp; fishing, and outdoor sports.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSee the Lifestyle of the Future: From modular homes to eco-friendly solutions, experience firsthand the new lifestyle trends of modern man in harmony with nature.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWitness Regional Power: Be a firsthand witness to Adana becoming the largest hobby and outdoor trade center in the region.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Adventure Redefined in Adana in April!</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to the unforgettable parade and colorful events of the Orange Blossom Carnival, be sure to visit HobbyPort Mediterranean, where you\'ll find answers to your passions. This year, Adana is not just a carnival city; it\'s a meeting point for freedom, hobbies, and nature!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Date:</strong>&nbsp;April 2-5, 2026<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Location:</strong>&nbsp;Adana International Fair and Congress Center</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We invite all our carnival friends to experience this unique synergy firsthand and add a new color to their lives!</p>\";s:8:\"location\";N;s:5:\"video\";N;s:15:\"youtubeplaylist\";N;s:3:\"ses\";N;s:7:\"spotify\";N;s:5:\"image\";s:48:\"bu-yil-nisanda-adanada-cosku-daha-da-artiyor.jpg\";s:4:\"icon\";N;s:4:\"file\";N;s:7:\"is_main\";i:0;s:8:\"blade_id\";i:33;s:11:\"category_id\";i:11;s:14:\"translation_of\";i:156;s:11:\"parent_page\";i:258;s:7:\"lang_id\";i:2;s:11:\"form_active\";i:0;s:9:\"published\";i:1;s:9:\"show_menu\";i:0;s:13:\"show_homepage\";i:0;s:11:\"show_footer\";i:0;s:15:\"show_sponsorluk\";i:0;s:10:\"created_at\";s:19:\"2026-04-30 14:12:23\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:19:\"2026-04-30 14:12:25\";s:10:\"deleted_at\";N;}s:11:\"\0*\0original\";a:34:{s:2:\"id\";i:262;s:3:\"hit\";N;s:8:\"sezon_id\";N;s:5:\"title\";s:51:\"The excitement is even greater in Adana this April!\";s:12:\"inside_title\";N;s:4:\"slug\";s:50:\"the-excitement-is-even-greater-in-adana-this-april\";s:4:\"link\";N;s:5:\"link2\";N;s:5:\"link3\";N;s:6:\"heyzen\";N;s:7:\"content\";s:2517:\"<p>The International Orange Blossom Carnival promises an unforgettable surprise for its visitors in 2026. HobbyPort Mediterranean Fair is included in the Carnival program as an associated event.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe energy of the Carnival transforms into a lifestyle festival with the HobbyPort Mediterranean Fair. Taking place in Adana from April 2-5, 2026, the HobbyPort Mediterranean Fair offers visitors the opportunity to discover their dream outdoor lifestyle and the latest hobby trends.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhile the Carnival represents fun, the streets, and togetherness, HobbyPort Mediterranean transforms this energy into personal passions and a desire to return to nature. The Carnival and HobbyPort create a synergy built on the philosophy of \"living life to the fullest.\" Visitors who will experience the carnival excitement in Adana amidst the scent of orange blossoms will also have the opportunity to discover their dream outdoor lifestyle and the latest hobby trends at the fairgrounds.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Why should Carnival visitors explore HobbyPort Mediterranean?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Complete Your Carnival Experience: Let the excitement of the streets continue with a passion for adventure! Crown the free spirit of the carnival with caravans, motorcycles, and outdoor equipment that will allow you to escape into nature.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDiscover the World of Hobbies: Not just for professionals; a wide range of inspiring content awaits visitors of all ages who want to make a fresh start, including caravans, tiny houses, hunting &amp; fishing, and outdoor sports.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSee the Lifestyle of the Future: From modular homes to eco-friendly solutions, experience firsthand the new lifestyle trends of modern man in harmony with nature.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWitness Regional Power: Be a firsthand witness to Adana becoming the largest hobby and outdoor trade center in the region.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Adventure Redefined in Adana in April!</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to the unforgettable parade and colorful events of the Orange Blossom Carnival, be sure to visit HobbyPort Mediterranean, where you\'ll find answers to your passions. This year, Adana is not just a carnival city; it\'s a meeting point for freedom, hobbies, and nature!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Date:</strong>&nbsp;April 2-5, 2026<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Location:</strong>&nbsp;Adana International Fair and Congress Center</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We invite all our carnival friends to experience this unique synergy firsthand and add a new color to their lives!</p>\";s:8:\"location\";N;s:5:\"video\";N;s:15:\"youtubeplaylist\";N;s:3:\"ses\";N;s:7:\"spotify\";N;s:5:\"image\";s:48:\"bu-yil-nisanda-adanada-cosku-daha-da-artiyor.jpg\";s:4:\"icon\";N;s:4:\"file\";N;s:7:\"is_main\";i:0;s:8:\"blade_id\";i:33;s:11:\"category_id\";i:11;s:14:\"translation_of\";i:156;s:11:\"parent_page\";i:258;s:7:\"lang_id\";i:2;s:11:\"form_active\";i:0;s:9:\"published\";i:1;s:9:\"show_menu\";i:0;s:13:\"show_homepage\";i:0;s:11:\"show_footer\";i:0;s:15:\"show_sponsorluk\";i:0;s:10:\"created_at\";s:19:\"2026-04-30 14:12:23\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:19:\"2026-04-30 14:12:25\";s:10:\"deleted_at\";N;}s:10:\"\0*\0changes\";a:0:{}s:11:\"\0*\0previous\";a:0:{}s:8:\"\0*\0casts\";a:1:{s:10:\"deleted_at\";s:8:\"datetime\";}s:17:\"\0*\0classCastCache\";a:0:{}s:21:\"\0*\0attributeCastCache\";a:0:{}s:13:\"\0*\0dateFormat\";N;s:10:\"\0*\0appends\";a:0:{}s:19:\"\0*\0dispatchesEvents\";a:0:{}s:14:\"\0*\0observables\";a:0:{}s:12:\"\0*\0relations\";a:0:{}s:10:\"\0*\0touches\";a:0:{}s:27:\"\0*\0relationAutoloadCallback\";N;s:26:\"\0*\0relationAutoloadContext\";N;s:10:\"timestamps\";b:1;s:13:\"usesUniqueIds\";b:0;s:9:\"\0*\0hidden\";a:0:{}s:10:\"\0*\0visible\";a:0:{}s:11:\"\0*\0fillable\";a:29:{i:0;s:3:\"hit\";i:1;s:8:\"sezon_id\";i:2;s:5:\"title\";i:3;s:12:\"inside_title\";i:4;s:4:\"slug\";i:5;s:4:\"link\";i:6;s:5:\"link2\";i:7;s:5:\"link3\";i:8;s:6:\"heyzen\";i:9;s:7:\"content\";i:10;s:8:\"location\";i:11;s:5:\"video\";i:12;s:3:\"ses\";i:13;s:7:\"spotify\";i:14;s:5:\"image\";i:15;s:4:\"icon\";i:16;s:4:\"file\";i:17;s:7:\"is_main\";i:18;s:8:\"blade_id\";i:19;s:11:\"category_id\";i:20;s:14:\"translation_of\";i:21;s:11:\"parent_page\";i:22;s:7:\"lang_id\";i:23;s:11:\"form_active\";i:24;s:9:\"published\";i:25;s:13:\"show_homepage\";i:26;s:11:\"show_footer\";i:27;s:15:\"show_sponsorluk\";i:28;s:9:\"show_menu\";}s:10:\"\0*\0guarded\";a:1:{i:0;s:1:\"*\";}s:16:\"\0*\0forceDeleting\";b:0;}i:172;O:15:\"App\\Models\\Page\":34:{s:13:\"\0*\0connection\";s:5:\"mysql\";s:8:\"\0*\0table\";s:5:\"pages\";s:13:\"\0*\0primaryKey\";s:2:\"id\";s:10:\"\0*\0keyType\";s:3:\"int\";s:12:\"incrementing\";b:1;s:7:\"\0*\0with\";a:0:{}s:12:\"\0*\0withCount\";a:0:{}s:19:\"preventsLazyLoading\";b:0;s:10:\"\0*\0perPage\";i:15;s:6:\"exists\";b:1;s:18:\"wasRecentlyCreated\";b:0;s:28:\"\0*\0escapeWhenCastingToString\";b:0;s:13:\"\0*\0attributes\";a:34:{s:2:\"id\";i:263;s:3:\"hit\";N;s:8:\"sezon_id\";N;s:5:\"title\";s:34:\"Carnival Program is now available!\";s:12:\"inside_title\";N;s:4:\"slug\";s:33:\"carnival-program-is-now-available\";s:4:\"link\";N;s:5:\"link2\";N;s:5:\"link3\";N;s:6:\"heyzen\";N;s:7:\"content\";s:745:\"<h2>The excitement of the 14th International Orange Blossom Carnival is about to begin!</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Between April 1st and 5th, Adana will host a packed program of events, from sporting activities and concerts to exhibitions and cultural and artistic performances. The colorful events, appealing to visitors of all ages from children to young people and women, will create unforgettable moments for guests from both within Turkey and abroad. You can view the detailed event program on our website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"medya/2026-portakal-cicegi-karnavali-programi.pdf\" style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 20px;  color:#e28337; padding: 5px 0; border-radius: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 600;\">Click here to download the program.</a></p>\";s:8:\"location\";N;s:5:\"video\";N;s:15:\"youtubeplaylist\";N;s:3:\"ses\";N;s:7:\"spotify\";N;s:5:\"image\";s:34:\"karnaval-programi-yayinda-yfz3.jpg\";s:4:\"icon\";N;