(146, 8, NULL, 'Sürdürülebilirlik Podcastleri', NULL, 'surdurulebilirlik-podcastleri', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı Sürdürülebilirlik Podcast sayfası, etkinliğin çevresel etkilerini azaltma, sosyal sorumluluk projelerine katkı sağlama ve sürdürülebilirlik hedeflerine ulaşma konularında uzmanlarla yapılan derinlemesine sohbetleri sunuyor. Her bölüm, karnavalın sürdürülebilirlik yolculuğunu, yenilikçi projeleri ve gelecekteki planlarını dinleyicilere aktarıyor.</p>\n\n<h2>Originnovation Podcast Yayınında Karnaval Sürdürülebilirlik&nbsp;Çalışmaları</h2>\n\n<p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/4vVZFvrb78OeYsGuPXO0CP?utm_source=generator\" style=\"border-radius:12px\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></p>\n\n<h2>TRT Çukurova Radyosu yayınında Karnaval Sürdürülebilirlik&nbsp;Çalışmaları</h2>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'surdurulebilirlik-podcastleri-ses-xkpv.mp3', NULL, 'surdurulebilirlik-podcastleri.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 5, NULL, 13, 1, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-03 05:26:06', '2026-04-30 11:56:14', NULL),
(147, NULL, NULL, 'Duyurular', NULL, 'duyurular', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(253, 253, 253); color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family:manrope,serif; font-size:18px\">Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı’nın her yıl daha da genişleyen etkinlik takvimini, ödüllü yarışmalarını ve diğer önemli duyurularını takip etmek için sayfamızı ziyaret edebilirsiniz.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 32, 2, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-03 06:20:28', '2026-04-30 11:49:33', NULL),
(148, 2, NULL, 'Ace Of Mice En İyi Kültür Ve Sanat Etkinliği Ödülü Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı', NULL, 'ace-of-mice-en-iyi-kultur-ve-sanat-etkinligi-odulu-portakal-cicegi-karnavali', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><strong><em>TEBRİKLER ADANA, TEŞEKKÜRLER ADANA!</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>ULUSLARARASI PORTAKAL ÇİÇEĞİ KARNAVALINA BİR ÖDÜL DAHA</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı, turizm ve etkinlik sektörünün “Oscar”ları olarak kabul edilen “Masters of Events by ACE of M.I.C.E. Awards” yarışmasında 2024 yılının En İyi Kültür ve Sanat Etkinliği ödülüne layık görüldü.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bu yılki yarışmaya rekor seviyede başvuru yapıldı. Turizm ve etkinlik sektörünün önde gelen isimlerinden oluşan 60 kişilik jüri heyeti yılın en iyilerini değerlendirdi.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'karnavalin-enerjisini-yakalamaya-hazir-misin-clri.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 2, NULL, 147, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-03 08:03:18', '2026-04-26 16:57:33', NULL),
(149, 4, NULL, '2024 Sürdürülebilirlik Raporları', NULL, '2024-surdurulebilirlik-raporlari', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'karnaval-programi-yayinda-p1xw.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 2, NULL, 147, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-03 08:05:47', '2026-04-26 16:57:25', NULL),
(150, NULL, NULL, 'Sürdürülebilirlik Videosu ve Sürdürülebilirlik Anket Yayınlandı!', NULL, 'surdurulebilirlik-videosu-ve-surdurulebilirlik-anket-yayinlandi', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Türkiye’nin en önemli markalarından biri olan Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı, yalnızca kültürel zenginliği ve renkli atmosferiyle değil, aynı zamanda sürdürülebilirlik alanındaki öncü çalışmalarıyla da dikkat çekiyor. Sürdürülebilirlik Koordinatörü Prof. Dr. Canan Madran’ın rehberliğinde gerçekleştirilen “çevre dostu” etkinlikler, ziyaretçilerin büyük beğenisini kazandı.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Atatürk Parkı’nda yürütülen “sürdürülebilirlik” faaliyetleri, somut verilerle de etkisini ortaya koydu. Parkta hayata geçirilen uygulamalara yönelik olarak 273 kişiyle yüz yüze yapılan ankette, genel memnuniyet oranı %82 olarak belirlendi. Katılımcıların %75’inden fazlası, park alanında yer alan tüm sürdürülebilirlik çalışmalarını “var, uygulandı, gördüm” şeklinde değerlendirdi. Bu sonuçlar, karnavalın çevresel farkındalık oluşturma hedefinde önemli bir adım attığını ortaya koyuyor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sürdürebilirlik Anketine ve Videosuna Buradan Ulaşabilirsiniz.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'bu-yil-nisanda-adanada-cosku-daha-da-artiyor-u1m6.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 2, NULL, 147, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-03 08:13:52', '2026-04-26 16:57:25', NULL),
(151, 8, NULL, 'Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı Tarihi Belli Oldu', NULL, 'uluslararasi-portakal-cicegi-karnavali-tarihi-belli-oldu', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>2026 yılında 14’üncüsü düzenlenecek Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı’nın tarihi açıklandı. 1-5 Nisan 2026 tarihleri arasında gerçekleştirilecek etkinliğe, yurt içinden ve yurt dışından yüzbinlerce kişinin katılması bekleniyor. Kültür ve sanat şölenine dönüşecek karnaval kapsamında büyük kortej yürüyüşü 4 Nisan 2026 tarihinde yapılacak.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'uluslararasi-portakal-cicegi-karnavali-tarihi-belli-oldu-vagx.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 2, NULL, 147, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-03 08:21:29', '2026-04-30 11:15:52', NULL),
(152, 10, NULL, 'Karnaval ruhu bu yıl doğaya da hayat veriyor!', NULL, 'karnaval-ruhu-bu-yil-dogaya-da-hayat-veriyor', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı, sürdürülebilirlik çalışmalarına bir yenisini daha ekleyerek Karnaval Hatıra Ormanı projesini hayata geçiriyor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Adana’nın 2 farklı bölgesinde 2026 yılında oluşturulacak bu özel hatıra ormanı, hem geleceğe nefes olacak hem de karnavalın doğaya olan sevgisini taçlandıracak.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>14. Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Geleceğe nefes olacak bu proje için hazır olun!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1–5 Nisan 2026</strong></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'karnaval-ruhu-bu-yil-dogaya-da-hayat-veriyor.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 2, NULL, 147, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-03 08:23:34', '2026-04-30 10:10:55', NULL),
(153, 12, NULL, 'Karnaval Bülteni', NULL, 'karnaval-bulteni', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(253, 253, 253); color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family:manrope,serif; font-size:18px\">Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı’nın birbirinden renkli kültür ve sanat etkinlikleriyle dolu Karnaval Bülteni’ne ulaşmak ve güncel konulardan haberdar olmak isterseniz formu doldurarak ücretsiz abone olabilirsiniz.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'karnaval-bulteni.png', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 2, NULL, 147, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-03 08:29:32', '2026-04-30 10:11:08', NULL),
(154, 14, NULL, 'Karnaval 2025 Ödülleri', NULL, 'karnaval-2025-odulleri', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Gururla Sunarız!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı için 2025 yılı ödüllerle taçlandı.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GIGI Awards, Dünya Gazetesi ve İstanbul Marketing Awards’ta kazandığımız ödüllerle bu büyük başarının gururunu yaşıyoruz. Bu yolculukta emeği geçen herkese ve her zaman yanımızda olan Adana halkına teşekkür ederiz. Birlikte daha nice başarılara!</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'karnaval-2025-odulleri-zijb.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 2, NULL, 147, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-03 08:32:52', '2026-04-26 16:57:23', NULL),
(155, 16, NULL, 'Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı Hatıra Ormanları Hayata Geçti!', NULL, 'uluslararasi-portakal-cicegi-karnavali-hatira-ormanlari-hayata-gecti', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Çukurova ve Karataş ilçelerinde oluşturulan 2 adet Karnaval Hatıra Ormanı ile geleceğe nefes olduk.<br />\r\nDaha yeşil bir Adana için doğaya değer katmaya, sürdürülebilir projeler üretmeye devam edeceğiz.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bu anlamlı çalışmaya verdikleri destek için Adana Orman Müdürlüğü’ne teşekkür ederiz.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'uluslararasi-portakal-cicegi-karnavali-hatira-ormanlari-hayata-gecti-nqc2.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 2, NULL, 147, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-03 08:38:31', '2026-04-30 11:15:04', NULL),
(156, 18, NULL, 'Bu yıl Nisan’da Adana’da coşku daha da artıyor!', NULL, 'bu-yil-nisanda-adanada-cosku-daha-da-artiyor', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı, 2026 yılında ziyaretçilerine unutulmaz bir sürpriz sunuyor. HobbyPort Akdeniz Fuarı, bağlı etkinlik olarak Karnaval programında yer alıyor.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nKarnaval’ın enerjisi, HobbyPort Akdeniz Fuarı ile bir yaşam tarzı festivaline dönüşüyor. Adana’da 2-5 Nisan 2026 tarihlerinde gerçekleşecek HobbyPort Akdeniz Fuarı, ziyaretçilere hayallerindeki outdoor yaşamı ve en yeni hobi trendlerini keşfetme imkanı veriyor.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nKarnaval; eğlenceyi, sokağı ve birlikteliği temsil ederken; HobbyPort Akdeniz, bu enerjiyi kişisel tutkulara ve doğaya dönüş arzusuna dönüştürüyor. Karnaval ve HobbyPort, \"hayatı dolu dolu yaşama\" felsefesi üzerine kurulu bir sinerjiyi meydana getiriyor. Portakal çiçeği kokuları arasında Adana\'da karnaval coşkusunu yaşayacak olan ziyaretçiler, fuar alanında da hayallerindeki outdoor yaşamı ve en yeni hobi trendlerini keşfetme imkanı bulacaklar.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Karnaval Ziyaretçileri Neden HobbyPort Akdeniz’i Gezmeli?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Karnaval Deneyimini Tamamlayın: Sokaklardaki coşku, macera tutkusu ile devam etsin! Karnavalın özgür ruhunu, doğada özgürleşmenizi sağlayacak karavanlar, motosikletler ve outdoor ekipmanlarıyla taçlandırın.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHobi Dünyasıyla Tanışın: Sadece profesyoneller için değil; yeni bir başlangıç yapmak isteyen her yaştan ziyaretçi için karavanlar, tiny houselar, avcılık &amp; balıkçılık ve doğa sporları gibi geniş bir yelpazede ilham verici içerikler sizi bekliyor.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGeleceğin Yaşam Biçimini Görün: Modüler evlerden doğa dostu çözümlere kadar, modern insanın doğayla barışık yeni yaşam trendlerini yerinde deneyimleyin.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBölgesel Güce Şahitlik Edin: Adana’nın bölgedeki en büyük hobi ve outdoor ticaret merkezi oluşuna ilk elden tanık olun.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>\"Nisan’da Adana’da\" Macera Yeniden Tanımlanıyor!</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı’nın unutulmaz korteji ve renkli etkinliklerinin yanı sıra, tutkularınıza yanıt bulacağınız HobbyPort Akdeniz durağına mutlaka uğrayın. Bu yıl Adana, sadece bir karnaval şehri değil; özgürlüğün, hobinin ve doğanın buluşma noktası!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Tarih: </strong>2-5 Nisan 2026<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Yer:</strong> Adana Uluslararası Fuar ve Kongre Merkezi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tüm karnaval dostlarımızı, bu eşsiz sinerjiyi yerinde yaşamaya ve hayatlarına yeni bir renk katmaya davet ediyoruz!</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'bu-yil-nisanda-adanada-cosku-daha-da-artiyor.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 2, NULL, 147, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-03 08:41:50', '2026-04-30 10:11:26', NULL),
(157, 20, NULL, 'Karnaval Programı Yayında!', NULL, 'karnaval-programi-yayinda', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<h2>14. Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı coşkusu başlıyor!</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>1-5 Nisan tarihleri arasında gerçekleşecek bu büyük etkinlikte Adana; sportif aktivitelerden konserlere, sergilerden kültür ve sanat gösterilerine kadar dopdolu bir programa ev sahipliği yapacak. Çocuklardan gençlere, kadınlardan her yaştan ziyaretçiye hitap eden rengârenk organizasyonlar, hem yurt içinden hem de yurt dışından gelen konuklara unutulmaz anlar yaşatacak. Karnavalın detaylı etkinlik programını sayfamızdan inceleyebilirsiniz.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'karnaval-programi-yayinda-yfz3.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 2, NULL, 147, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-03 08:43:30', '2026-04-30 11:14:09', NULL),
(158, 22, NULL, 'Karnavalın Enerjisini Yakalamaya Hazır Mısın?', NULL, 'karnavalin-enerjisini-yakalamaya-hazir-misin', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı kapsamında düzenlenen fotoğraf ve video yarışması başlıyor!<br />\r\n<strong>1–5 Nisan 2026</strong><br />\r\nHer gün yeni kareler, yeni hikâyeler!</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'karnavalin-enerjisini-yakalamaya-hazir-misin.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 2, NULL, 147, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-03 08:46:20', '2026-04-30 10:11:59', NULL),
(163, NULL, NULL, 'About the Orange Blossom Carnival', NULL, 'about-the-orange-blossom-carnival', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Adana is one of the most beautiful cities in April…</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Every street is filled with the sweet scent of orange blossoms...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The scent of orange blossoms is enchanting...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It cleanses your soul,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You feel rejuvenated,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You feel purified…</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For instance, it can make a person forgive even their most estranged old friend, and it’s a bit dangerous too; it can make a person fall in love with the very first person they see on the street.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>April is the most beautiful season in Adana…&nbsp;<strong>Orange Blossom&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>season… The climate transforms into something incredibly beautiful. Neither cold nor hot… The air feels just like “lemonade.”</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You put on your short-sleeved shirts and head out into the street. As you walk the same streets as Adana’s warm, friendly people, that magnificent scent of orange blossoms, carried by the wind now and then, never leaves your side for 24 hours a day. It leaves you spellbound…</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No matter where in Turkey or the world they live, Adanalıs always come to Adana during the orange blossom season. To not miss out on this excitement, which lasts only once a year for at most 3–4 weeks…</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The orange blossom season generally lasts throughout April, though it may vary by a few days depending on the weather. This site was created to promote this incredible experience so that everyone can enjoy it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please mark your calendars now for next April. We especially invite you all to Adana to experience this unforgettable moment during April, when the orange blossoms are at their peak.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'portakal-cicegi-karnavali-hakkinda-pjec.png', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 1, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-06 05:05:02', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(164, NULL, NULL, 'Who is Ali Haydar Bozkurt?', NULL, 'who-is-ali-haydar-bozkurt', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>I was born in 1967. I spent the first 29 years of my life in Adana, where the streets smell of orange blossoms in April.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>During this time, alongside my education, I worked professionally in theater. I also played licensed basketball for many years. I devoted a considerable amount of time to hobbies such as photography, music, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I continue to visit Adana regularly at certain intervals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, especially every April — or as we, the lovers of Adana, call it, the Orange Blossom Season — no matter where I am in the world, I always make sure to come to Adana. There was only one year I couldn’t do this. That year, thankfully, my teacher and dear friends collected orange blossoms, placed them in jars, and sent them to me by cargo. I kept those jars in my refrigerator for a week. Every morning and evening, I would open the jars, smell them, close my eyes, and imagine myself walking through the streets of Adana in April. It may be a bit difficult to explain this to someone who has never experienced it before. But for those who have, it is a beauty that stays with them for a lifetime.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Every April, I go to Adana and, especially in the late afternoon hours when the scent of orange blossoms is at its peak, I put on my jeans, my t-shirt, and my indispensable white Converse, and head out to the city streets. These walks are something I never get tired of or bored with… Every place I pass holds a different memory... In the background, waves of that magnificent orange blossom scent… That magical fragrance that cleanses my soul enough to make me love everyone and everything…</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When we were children, there were orange groves very close to the city center in Adana, and in the evenings, the wind would carry the scent of orange blossoms from those groves into the streets of the city. It would hit our faces in waves wherever it passed… Now, the orange groves in the city center may no longer exist, but thanks to the orange (bitter orange) trees on every street and the trees in the parks in the city center, you can still find the same scent on every street you walk.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>I had a socially, artistically, and sports-oriented educational life in Adana. I am a graduate of Ayas College. In fact, I am one of the first male graduates of the school. There were only 2 male students in our class. Our only problem was that we had to form mixed teams with girls because we couldn’t form a boys’ basketball team for inter-class matches. We were lucky… We had memories to tell for a lifetime and friendships that would last forever.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I never left Adana during my university years and graduated from Çukurova University, Department of Business Administration (English).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Throughout my entire education life, I never studied lessons. My time outside of classes was so full with activities like theater, basketball, music, and photography that I had no time to study, so I tried to learn by listening carefully during lessons. Despite this, I believe I was a successful student.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In 1996 (I was 29 years old at the time), although somewhat late, I moved to Istanbul to start my professional career.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>During this time, I held various positions in different companies. I am currently serving as the CEO of Toyota Turkey. At the same time, I also serve as the CEO of ALJ Mobility Europe and Turkey.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I believe that success comes from “making a difference” and that the most fundamental element for achieving all goodness and beauty in the world is effective communication.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For all these reasons, I wanted to share with you the unique and distinctive beauties of Adana. The main purpose of establishing this website is to introduce Adana’s lesser-known orange blossom season and its beauties to as many people as possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With this in mind, we set out with the slogan “In Adana in April!”. With the support of all friends, whether from Adana or not, we aim to grow this movement and ensure that more people visit Adana every April to experience this incredible atmosphere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This invitation has no political or commercial purpose whatsoever. By preserving our sensitivity on this matter, we simply want to create something out of “love” and invite everyone who wishes to experience this beauty with us in Adana in April.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Although the orange blossom season may vary by a few days each year depending on the climate, it generally falls between April 5–20. For this reason, we invite you to join us during the first week of April, when the scent of orange blossoms is at its most intense. Of course, I would also recommend that you do not plan just a one-day visit. In the relevant section of this website, I will try to provide you with detailed information on “What to Do in Adana”.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'ali-haydar-bozkurt-kimdir.png', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 2, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-06 05:15:24', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(173, NULL, NULL, 'Adana Flavors', 'Adana Flavors', 'adana-flavors', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Adana, which has become a brand in the field of gastronomy, promotes its culinary culture to the world with its traditional Flavor Festival. Delicious local tastes such as Adana kebab, lahmacun, bici bici dessert, sıkma-ayran, şalgam, şırdan, and yüksük çorbası bring visitors together with a wonderful feast of flavors during the carnival.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 4, 8, 96, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2026-04-07 07:35:16', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(180, 12, NULL, 'Karnaval Gazetesi', NULL, 'karnaval-gazetesi', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Binlerce yıllık kültürel mirasın harmanlandığı Adana, her yıl milyonlarca yerli ve yabancı turisti “sevgi, dostluk ve kardeşlik” atmosferinde buluşturan “Nisan’da Adana’da” Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı’na ev sahipliği yapıyor. Tiyatrodan operaya, konserlerden sinemaya kadar geniş etkinlik yelpazesine sahip olan karnaval, yerel ve ulusal basında geniş yer buluyor. Karnaval ile ilgili haberleri sayfamızda inceleyebilirsiniz.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 17, 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2026-04-02 02:17:48', '2026-04-30 11:54:38', NULL),
(181, 24, NULL, '2024 Karnaval Gazetesi', NULL, '2024-karnaval-gazetesi', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://heyzine.com/flip-book/ff05d61054.html', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-karnaval-gazetesi-lgsn.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 18, 1, NULL, 180, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-02 02:53:31', '2026-04-19 12:19:43', NULL),
(182, 26, NULL, '2025 Karnaval Gazetesi', NULL, '2025-karnaval-gazetesi', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://heyzine.com/flip-book/67e27ed099.html', '<p>2025 Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı Gazetesi’ni sayfamızda inceleyebilirsiniz.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-karnaval-gazetesi-z8oi.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 18, 1, NULL, 180, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-02 02:56:57', '2026-04-19 12:20:01', NULL),
(183, NULL, NULL, 'Karnaval Haritası', NULL, 'karnaval-haritasi', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>2026 Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı haritası ile etkinliklerimizi daha kolay takip&nbsp;edebilirsiniz.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe height=\"1000\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/1/embed?mid=1tcyjTOsXNVpFFlv6LLI3FAqILhHaDbY&amp;ehbc=2E312F\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 31, 6, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-26 16:54:07', '2026-04-30 11:57:02', NULL),
(184, NULL, NULL, 'İletişim', NULL, 'iletisim', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı etkinlikleriyle ilgili sorularınızı sormak, talep ve önerilerinizi paylaşmak için sayfamızdaki formu doldurarak bizimle iletişime geçebilirsiniz.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 7, 3, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-27 12:04:17', '2026-04-27 12:04:17', NULL),
(185, NULL, NULL, 'Sponsorluk', NULL, 'sponsorluk', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div class=\"sponsorluk-sunumu \">\r\n<div class=\"max-width\">\r\n<h2>SPONSORLUK İÇİN İLETİŞİME GEÇİN</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Sponsor olmak için ve detaylı bilgi almak için aşağıda bulunan iletişim yöntemlerini kullanabilirsiniz.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"iletisim-butonlari\"><a class=\"iletisim-buton tel\" href=\"tel:+905322978601\">Telefon</a> <a class=\"iletisim-buton mail\" href=\"mailto:sponsorluk@nisandaadanada.com\">E-mail</a> <a class=\"iletisim-buton wp\" href=\"https://wa.me/+905322978601?text=Bilgi%20almak%20istiyorum\">Whatsapp</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2>2026 KARNAVAL SPONSORLUK DOSYASI</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"sponsorlarimiz-list\"><a class=\"sponsorlarimiz-buton\" href=\"karnaval-sponsorluk-dosyasi\" target=\"_blank\">KARNAVAL SPONSORLUK DOSYASI</a></div>\r\n\r\n<h2>2025 PR RAPORU</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"sponsorlarimiz-list\"><a class=\"sponsorlarimiz-buton\" href=\"pr-raporu\" target=\"_blank\">PR RAPORU</a></div>\r\n\r\n<h2>2025 KARNAVAL TANITIM FİLMİ</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"sponsorlarimiz-list\"><a class=\"sponsorlarimiz-buton\" href=\"karnaval-tanitim-filmi\" target=\"_blank\">KARNAVAL TANITIM FİLMİ</a></div>\r\n\r\n<h2>2025 Resmi Destekçi ve Sponsorlarımız</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"sponsorlarimiz-list\"><a class=\"sponsorlarimiz-buton\" href=\"2025-yili-resmi-destekci-ve-sponsorlarimiz\" target=\"_blank\">2025 Resmi Destekçi ve Sponsorlarımız</a></div>\r\n\r\n<h2>Ulusal ve Bölgesel Sponsorluk Satışı ve Pazarlaması\'ndan Sorumlu Yetkili Ajanslar</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"sponsorlarimiz-list\"><a class=\"sponsorlarimiz-buton\" href=\"yetkili-ajanslar\" target=\"_blank\">Yetkili Ajanslar</a></div>\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 34, 13, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-27 13:47:27', '2026-04-27 13:56:41', NULL),
(186, NULL, NULL, 'Karnaval Sponsorluk Dosyası', NULL, 'karnaval-sponsorluk-dosyasi', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Türkiye’nin ve dünyanın dört bir yanından gelen yüz binlerce ziyaretçinin katılımıyla gerçekleşen Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı’nın heyecanına ortak olabilir ve etkinliğe değer katacak sponsor seçenekleri arasında yer alabilirsiniz.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>2026 KARNAVAL SPONSORLUK DOSYASI</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe class=\"fp-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://heyzine.com/flip-book/5615b7d81a.html\" style=\"border: 1px solid lightgray; width: 100%; height: 768px;\"></iframe></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 31, 13, NULL, 185, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-27 14:00:30', '2026-04-27 14:01:14', NULL),
(187, NULL, NULL, 'PR Raporu', NULL, 'pr-raporu', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı’nın yazılı, dijital ve görsel basın ile sosyal medyadaki paylaşımlarına ilişkin detaylı veriler için 2025 PR Raporu’nu inceleyebilirsiniz.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>2025 PR RAPORU</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe class=\"fp-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://heyzine.com/flip-book/edbf362b71.html\" style=\"border: 1px solid lightgray; width: 100%; height: 768px;\"></iframe></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 31, 13, NULL, 185, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-27 14:02:00', '2026-04-27 14:02:00', NULL),
(188, NULL, NULL, 'Yetkili Ajanslar', NULL, 'yetkili-ajanslar', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Uluslararası Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı’nın ulusal sponsorluk satışları ve pazarlama faaliyetlerinden sorumlu yetkili ajansları sayfamızda inceleyebilirsiniz.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 36, 13, NULL, 185, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-27 14:07:07', '2026-04-27 14:07:07', NULL),
(189, NULL, NULL, 'Past Years', 'Past Years', 'past-years', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The International Orange Blossom Carnival, which holds the distinction of being Turkey\'s first and only street carnival, has been hosting thousands of participants from within the country and abroad since 2013. You can find the data for this unique event, which has broken records, on our page.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 12, 7, 3, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:12:12', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(190, NULL, NULL, 'Photo Archive', 'Photo Archive', 'photo-archive', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>You can view images of the International Orange Blossom Carnival, which transforms the streets and avenues of Adana into a festival with colorful costumes every April, on our page.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 13, 7, 19, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:12:54', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(191, NULL, NULL, 'Video Archive', NULL, 'video-archive', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Visit our page to watch promotional videos, news, and event videos of the International Orange Blossom Carnival, one of Türkiye\'s most valuable brands.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 15, 7, 34, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:13:10', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(192, NULL, NULL, 'Carnival Newspaper', NULL, 'carnival-newspaper', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Adana, a city where thousands of years of cultural heritage are blended, hosts the \"Adana in April\" International Orange Blossom Carnival every year, bringing together millions of domestic and foreign tourists in an atmosphere of \"love, friendship, and brotherhood.\" With a wide range of events from theater and opera to concerts and cinema, the carnival receives extensive coverage in local and national media. You can find news about the carnival on our page.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 17, 7, 180, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:16:47', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(193, NULL, NULL, 'Carnival Song', NULL, 'carnival-song', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>You too can join in the carnival excitement with the song \"Nisan\'da Adana\'da Dökülün Sokaklara\" (Pour into the Streets of Adana in April), written and composed by Ezgi Özbay and arranged by Suat Aydoğan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Take to the streets in Adana in April!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pour into the streets and whistle!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Join us in singing this carnival song,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let\'s sing together and let our hearts rejoice!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let all of Türkiye hear the orange blossom!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IN ADANA IN APRIL,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LET\'S HAVE FUN AT THE CARNIVAL!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>LET\'S PLAY LOUDLY AND BANGING!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>NOW LET\'S WHISTLE.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lyrics and Music: Ezgi Özbay</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Edited by: Suat Aydoğan</strong></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'karnaval-sarkisi.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 55, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:17:32', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(194, NULL, NULL, 'Press Room', NULL, 'press-room', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Throughout the event, the carnival, with its diverse and colorful activities, was closely followed by local and national media. You can review written and visual news about the carnival on our page.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 19, 7, 57, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:17:55', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(195, NULL, NULL, 'Frequently Asked Questions', NULL, 'frequently-asked-questions', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div class=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Manrope, serif; transition: 0.3s ease-in-out; max-width: calc(100% - 350px); width: 990px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">\r\n<p>The Orange Blossom Carnival, one of the country\'s leading cultural and artistic events, attracts thousands of local and international tourists. You can find answers to frequently asked questions about this event, whose fame extends beyond the country\'s borders, on our page.</p>\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 59, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:18:21', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(196, NULL, NULL, '2026 Carnival Program', NULL, '2026-carnival-program', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 60, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:18:40', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(197, NULL, NULL, 'Our sponsors', NULL, 'our-sponsors', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The International Orange Blossom Carnival, one of Adana\'s shining brands, hosts even more spectacular events with the support of its strong sponsors. You can discover the sponsors who add value to the carnival on our page.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"resmi-destekci-sponsorlar\" style=\"margin: 50px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Manrope, serif; transition: 0.3s ease-in-out; width: 1390px; display: flex; justify-content: start; align-items: start; gap: 25px; flex-wrap: wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">&nbsp;</div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 20, 7, 74, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:19:40', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(198, NULL, NULL, 'Orange Blossom Carnival 2013', NULL, 'orange-blossom-carnival-2013', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<div class=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Manrope, serif; transition: 0.3s ease-in-out; max-width: calc(100% - 350px); width: 990px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(253, 253, 253); color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:manrope,serif; font-size:medium\">The carnival first took place on April 12-14, 2013. Reaching 100,000 participants, the 1st International Orange Blossom Carnival opened in 2013 with a parade attended by approximately 15,000 people from Adana and beyond.</span></div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2013-yilinda-portakal-cicegi-karnavali.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 18, 189, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:26:06', '2026-04-29 07:26:06', NULL),
(199, NULL, NULL, 'Orange Blossom Carnival 2014', NULL, 'orange-blossom-carnival-2014', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(253, 253, 253); color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family:manrope,serif; font-size:18px\">In its first year, 2013, 100,000 people watched the carnival events live, and in 2014, this number rose to 140,000. The carnival events, with approximately 15,000 people from Adana and other cities participating enthusiastically in the parade in 2013 and 30,000 in 2014, were met with great interest.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2014-yilinda-portakal-cicegi-karnavali.png', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 17, 189, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:26:42', '2026-04-29 07:26:42', NULL),
(200, NULL, NULL, 'Orange Blossom Carnival 2015', NULL, 'orange-blossom-carnival-2015', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(253, 253, 253); color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family:manrope,serif; font-size:18px\">Hotels are fully booked, extra flights and bus services are being arranged, and campsites are being set up for tents… This year\'s carnival broke records. According to official figures, 90,000 people attended, and attendance at the opening ceremony and concert reached 150,000. With around 350,000 people watching the events live, the carnival has thus become a major event known to almost everyone living in Türkiye.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-yilinda-portakal-cicegi-karnavali.png', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 16, 189, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:26:59', '2026-04-29 07:26:59', NULL),
(201, NULL, NULL, 'Orange Blossom Carnival 2016', NULL, 'orange-blossom-carnival-2016', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(253, 253, 253); color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family:manrope,serif; font-size:18px\">It is estimated that 20-25 thousand people stay overnight in Adana and its surroundings for the carnival, while the number of day-trippers from outside the city is around 75-80 thousand. In 2012, the total number of tourists staying in Adana was 544,065 (114,266 foreign and 429,799 domestic), while this number reached 911,000 in 2016.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-yilinda-portakal-cicegi-karnavali.png', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 15, 189, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:28:40', '2026-04-29 07:28:40', NULL),
(202, NULL, NULL, 'Orange Blossom Carnival 2017', NULL, 'orange-blossom-carnival-2017', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(253, 253, 253); color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family:manrope,serif; font-size:18px\">The \"International Orange Blossom Carnival,\" which has managed to become one of the world\'s leading carnivals, featured numerous cultural and artistic activities alongside its fun events. Accompanied by the scent of orange blossoms heralding spring, approximately 1.5 million people, including 100,000 from outside Adana, gathered in the streets of Adana to experience the great excitement.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-yilinda-portakal-cicegi-karnavali.png', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 14, 189, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:29:06', '2026-04-29 07:29:06', NULL),
(203, NULL, NULL, 'Orange Blossom Carnival 2018', NULL, 'orange-blossom-carnival-2018', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(253, 253, 253); color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family:manrope,serif; font-size:18px\">In Türkiye\'s first and only street carnival, as in previous years, 1.5 million people transformed the streets of Adana into a grand festival area. Participants in the carnival events shared in the great enthusiasm, and the people of Adana, dressed in colorful costumes, filled the streets and avenues, practically staying awake all weekend.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2018-yilinda-portakal-cicegi-karnavali.png', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 12, 189, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:29:22', '2026-04-29 07:29:22', NULL),
(204, NULL, NULL, 'Orange Blossom Carnival 2019', NULL, 'orange-blossom-carnival-2019', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(253, 253, 253); color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:manrope,serif; font-size:medium\">The carnival, now in its seventh year, took place between April 3-7, 2019. The Orange Blossom Carnival, which had a significant economic impact on Adana and the surrounding region, resulted in substantial increases in revenue for all hotels and restaurants, food and beverage establishments, shops, hundreds of small businesses with stalls, supermarkets, wholesalers and distributors, food producers, and even taxi drivers. The revitalization of domestic tourism through the carnival created a kind of domino effect in almost every sector of Adana\'s economy. It was reported that the carnival generated a total of 150 million TL in seasonal economic activity in Adana and surrounding cities.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-yilinda-portakal-cicegi-karnavali.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 10, 189, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:29:51', '2026-04-29 07:29:51', NULL),
(205, NULL, NULL, 'Orange Blossom Carnival 2020', NULL, 'orange-blossom-carnival-2020', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(253, 253, 253); color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:manrope,serif; font-size:medium\">The carnival was cancelled in 2020 due to the Covid-19 pandemic that affected the whole world. Many celebrities supported the carnival, which was held online instead.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2020-yilinda-portakal-cicegi-karnavali.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 9, 189, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:30:15', '2026-04-29 07:30:15', NULL),
(206, NULL, NULL, 'Orange Blossom Carnival 2021', NULL, 'orange-blossom-carnival-2021', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(253, 253, 253); color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:manrope,serif; font-size:medium\">Due to the ongoing Covid-19 pandemic, a hybrid carnival took place between April 1-4, 2021, both live online and with a limited number of participants taking part in their cars.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2021-yilinda-portakal-cicegi-karnavali.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 8, 189, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:30:28', '2026-04-29 07:30:28', NULL),
(207, NULL, NULL, 'Orange Blossom Carnival 2022', NULL, 'orange-blossom-carnival-2022', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(253, 253, 253); color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:manrope,serif; font-size:medium\">The carnival, in its tenth year, took place between March 23-27, 2022. It is estimated that approximately 300,000 carnival visitors from within Turkey and abroad spent an average of 500 TL per person. Considering accommodation, food and beverages, entertainment, shopping, and similar expenses, the contribution of visitors from outside Adana to the Adana economy is estimated to be around 150 million TL. Furthermore, taking into account the symbolic expenditure of approximately 200 TL per person by the approximately 1 million people from Adana attending the events during the carnival on food, beverages, entertainment, and shopping, it is seen that an internal trade volume of around 200 million TL was generated. When other expenses such as intercity air and land transportation, and intracity private and public transportation are added to all these figures, it has been reported that the Orange Blossom Carnival generated an economy of approximately 350 million TL.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-yilinda-portakal-cicegi-karnavali.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 7, 189, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:30:44', '2026-04-29 07:30:44', NULL),
(208, NULL, NULL, 'Orange Blossom Carnival 2023', NULL, 'orange-blossom-carnival-2023', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(253, 253, 253); color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:manrope,serif; font-size:medium\">Due to the earthquakes centered in Kahramanmaraş on February 6-7, 2023, and the subsequent floods, the festival committee, in a joint decision with the Ministry of Culture and Tourism, the Governorship of Adana, and the Metropolitan Municipality of Adana, cancelled the festival. We extend our deepest condolences to our entire nation for the loss of our citizens in this great earthquake, which plunged our country into deep mourning and caused numerous casualties in Adana.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-yilinda-portakal-cicegi-karnavali.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 6, 189, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:30:55', '2026-04-29 07:30:55', NULL),
(209, NULL, NULL, 'Orange Blossom Carnival 2024', NULL, 'orange-blossom-carnival-2024', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Our event is as follows:</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-yilinda-portakal-cicegi-karnavali.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 7, 5, 189, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 07:31:40', '2026-04-29 07:31:40', NULL),
(210, NULL, NULL, '2013 Photo Archive', NULL, '2013-photo-archive', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>You can view photos of the colorful and vibrant moments from the 2013 International Orange Blossom Carnival on our page.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2013-fotograf-arsivi.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 14, 7, 20, 190, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 08:01:32', '2026-04-29 08:01:32', NULL),
