(219, NULL, NULL, '2022 Photo Archive', NULL, '2022-photo-archive', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>You can view photos of the colorful and vibrant moments from the 2022 International Orange Blossom Carnival on our page.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"galeri-sayfasi\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Manrope, serif; transition: 0.3s ease-in-out; display: flex; justify-content: start; align-items: start; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">&nbsp;</div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-fotograf-arsivi.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 14, 7, 29, 190, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 08:04:58', '2026-04-29 08:04:58', NULL),
(220, NULL, NULL, '2024 Photo Archive', NULL, '2024-photo-archive', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>You can view photos of the colorful and vibrant moments from the 2024 International Orange Blossom Carnival on our page.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"galeri-sayfasi\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Manrope, serif; transition: 0.3s ease-in-out; display: flex; justify-content: start; align-items: start; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">&nbsp;</div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-fotograf-arsivi.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 14, 7, 31, 190, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 08:05:12', '2026-04-29 08:05:12', NULL),
(221, NULL, NULL, '2025 Photo Archive', NULL, '2025-photo-archive', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>You can view photos of the colorful and vibrant moments of the 2025 International Orange Blossom Carnival on our page.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-fotograf-arsivi.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 14, 7, 32, 190, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 08:05:28', '2026-04-29 08:05:28', NULL),
(222, NULL, NULL, 'Carnival Songs', NULL, 'carnival-songs', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'karnaval-sarkilari.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 16, 7, 35, 191, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 08:06:53', '2026-04-29 08:06:53', NULL),
(223, NULL, NULL, 'News Videos', NULL, 'news-videos', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'haber-videolari.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 16, 7, 36, 191, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 08:07:12', '2026-04-29 08:07:12', NULL),
(224, NULL, NULL, 'Promotional Videos', NULL, 'promotional-videos', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>You can watch promotional videos on our page featuring the colorful events of the International Orange Blossom Carnival, which brings millions of people of all ages together in the streets of Adana.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'tanitim-filmleri.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 16, 7, 37, 191, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 08:07:38', '2026-04-29 08:07:38', NULL),
(225, NULL, NULL, 'Carnival Promotional Video', NULL, 'carnival-promotional-video', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>You can watch the video content showcasing the vibrant and exciting events of the 2025 International Orange Blossom Carnival on our page.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 31, 7, 56, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 08:08:46', '2026-04-29 08:08:46', NULL),
(226, NULL, NULL, 'Carnival in Visual Media', NULL, 'carnival-in-visual-media', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>You can find news coverage of the International Orange Blossom Carnival, whose fame extends beyond national borders, broadcast on local and national television, on our website.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'gorsel-basinda-karnaval.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 16, 7, 58, 194, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-29 08:09:38', '2026-04-29 08:09:38', NULL),
(227, NULL, NULL, 'Around Adana', NULL, 'around-adana', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The International Orange Blossom Carnival brings thousands of visitors from all over Turkey and the world to Adana every year. This event, held within the scope of the Ministry of Culture and Tourism\'s \'Turkey Culture Route Festivals,\' offers participants not only entertainment but also an opportunity to explore the rich historical and tourist sites in Adana and its surroundings. During the carnival, guests can closely observe the iconic structures and natural beauties of Çukurova, from the Adana Museum to Anavarza Castle, from Ashab-ı Kehf to the Atatürk House Museum, and Belemedik Plateau. This special region, where history, culture, and nature intertwine, offers visitors unforgettable moments.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'adana-cevresi-icon-iinx.svg', NULL, 0, 22, 8, 91, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:43:16', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(228, NULL, NULL, 'Places to Visit in Tarsus', NULL, 'places-to-visit-in-tarsus', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>As part of the International Orange Blossom Carnival, Tarsus, with its 7,500 years of uninterrupted history, is one of the destinations worth exploring. This ancient city, bearing the traces of many deeply rooted civilizations, captivates its visitors with its unique historical structures and natural beauties. Among the main places to visit in Tarsus are important locations such as the Cave of Ashab-ı Kehf, the Tomb of Prophet Daniel, Cleopatra\'s Gate, St. Paul\'s Well, Tarsus Waterfall, and Kubatpaşa Madrasa. Tarsus, which stands out with its natural beauties as well as its historical texture, offers its visitors the opportunity to take a journey through time.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'tarsusta-gezilecek-yerler.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 25, 8, 92, 227, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:43:41', '2026-04-30 07:43:41', NULL),
(229, NULL, NULL, 'Places to Visit in Adana', NULL, 'places-to-visit-in-adana', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The International Orange Blossom Carnival has brought millions of people together under the umbrella of “love and friendship” since its organization in 2013. The carnival, which stands out with its culture, art, science, sports, gastronomy, and design activities, provides an opportunity to explore the city\'s historical heritage through its tour organizations. How about discovering Adana\'s numerous important historical and natural assets, from the Great Clock Tower to Kazancılar Bazaar, from Misis Bridge to Stone Bridge and Varda Bridge? With its rich cuisine and warm-hearted people, Adana offers its visitors an excellent experience throughout the carnival.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'adanada-gezilecek-yerler.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 23, 8, 93, 227, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:43:54', '2026-04-30 07:43:54', NULL),
(230, NULL, NULL, '1 Week Around Adana', NULL, '1-week-around-adana', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The International Orange Blossom Carnival offers participants exciting and enjoyable moments with its week-long travel programs. Thanks to tours covering Adana, Mersin, and Gaziantep, visitors have the opportunity to see the unique historical and cultural heritage of the region. As part of the travel organization, many unique experiences specific to the region, from ancient cities to natural beauties, from local cuisine to music, are provided together.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'adana-cevresinde-1-hafta-icon-n1kq.svg', NULL, 0, 26, 8, 94, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:45:45', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(231, NULL, NULL, 'Fish', NULL, 'fish', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Don\'t deprive yourself of the pleasure of eating fish and getting lost in the view in Adana.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'balik.avif', NULL, NULL, 0, 5, 8, 97, 173, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:47:00', '2026-04-30 07:47:00', NULL),
(232, NULL, NULL, 'Sweet', NULL, 'sweet', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Don\'t resist the sweets you come across while walking down the street. Allow yourself to be captivated by the sensation these uniquely delicious desserts, only available in Adana, leave on your palate.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'tatli.avif', NULL, NULL, 0, 5, 8, 98, 173, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:47:58', '2026-04-30 07:47:58', NULL),
(233, NULL, NULL, 'Hamburger ( Cheesburger)', NULL, 'hamburger-cheesburger', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Adana, which interprets every dish in its own way, adds the hamburger to its list and presents us with a version that you can only find in Adana.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'hamburger.avif', NULL, NULL, 0, 5, 8, 99, 173, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:49:26', '2026-04-30 07:49:26', NULL),
(234, NULL, NULL, 'Soup', NULL, 'soup', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The indispensable soups of the winter months warm us even more with Adana\'s unique interpretations. In Adana, before your kebabs, you must try the thimble soup, widow\'s soup, and mother and daughter soup. Also, after trying the trotters soup in Adana, you won\'t like it anywhere else.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'corba.avif', NULL, NULL, 0, 5, 8, 100, 173, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:49:53', '2026-04-30 07:49:53', NULL),
(235, NULL, NULL, 'Tripe', NULL, 'tripe', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Shirdan, made from the stomach of a lamb, is one of Adana\'s oldest and most traditional dishes. You can find shirdan vendors on almost every street corner, summer or winter. Sprinkling plenty of cumin on top will add a special flavor to your dish.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'sirdan.avif', NULL, NULL, 0, 5, 8, 102, 173, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:50:19', '2026-04-30 07:50:19', NULL),
(236, NULL, NULL, 'Pastry', NULL, 'pastry', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Adana börek, made with dough as thin as baklava dough, offers a feast of flavors with both its cheese and minced meat versions. When served, the thinly sliced ​​börek is always accompanied by sliced ​​tomatoes and pickles.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'borek.avif', NULL, NULL, 0, 5, 8, 103, 173, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:50:43', '2026-04-30 07:50:43', NULL),
(237, NULL, NULL, 'Turnip', NULL, 'turnip', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Made through fermentation, and developing its unique, slightly soda-like taste as it ferments, turnip juice is a drink you\'ll never have trouble finding in Adana. If you get the chance, you should definitely try tasting it with the pieces intact. A note: if you want to drink good turnip juice, choose one without added spice.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'salgam-qlpm.avif', NULL, NULL, 0, 5, 8, 104, 173, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:51:13', '2026-04-30 07:51:13', NULL),
(238, NULL, NULL, 'Inoculation', NULL, 'inoculation', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Licorice root sherbet is called \"aşlama\" in Adana and is especially popular for cooling down. Similar in taste to iced tea, aşlama is a favorite for its refreshing effect. You can find itinerant vendors carrying large copper jugs on their backs all over Adana.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'aslama.avif', NULL, NULL, 0, 5, 8, 105, 173, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:51:36', '2026-04-30 07:51:36', NULL),
(239, NULL, NULL, 'Bagel', NULL, 'bagel', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>This sugar-free, braided kazan simidi (a type of Turkish bagel) is baked in a stone oven and has won hearts with its unique Çukurova flavor.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'kazan-simidi.avif', NULL, NULL, 0, 5, 8, 106, 173, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:53:17', '2026-04-30 07:53:17', NULL),
(240, NULL, NULL, 'Squeezing', NULL, 'squeezing', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Often confused with gözleme (a type of Turkish flatbread), sıkma is a type of dough filled with ingredients such as cheese or potatoes. Especially enjoyed at breakfast with ayran (a yogurt drink), it\'s a great way to start your day off right.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'sikma.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 5, 8, 107, 173, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:53:45', '2026-04-30 07:53:45', NULL),
(241, NULL, NULL, 'BiciBici', NULL, 'bicibici', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Bici bici, a delicious dessert found only in Adana, is made from a mixture of grated ice, starch, powdered sugar, and syrup. Especially a number one refreshing treat in the summer months, bici bici, which used to be sold on the streets, can now be found all over Adana.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'bici-bici.avif', NULL, NULL, 0, 5, 8, 108, 173, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:54:34', '2026-04-30 07:54:34', NULL),
(242, NULL, NULL, 'Liver Kebab', NULL, 'liver-kebab', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>In Adana, breakfast is unthinkable without liver, a tradition that has become a hallmark of the city. Every Sunday, kebab vendors set up grills in the side streets around the historic Büyük Saat (Great Clock) have been serving hundreds of kilos of freshly cut liver to their customers for over a century.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'ciger-kebabi.avif', NULL, NULL, 0, 5, 8, 109, 173, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:55:02', '2026-04-30 07:55:02', NULL),
(243, NULL, NULL, 'Adana Lahmacun', NULL, 'adana-lahmacun', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Forget everything you know about lahmacun! Adana\'s lahmacun is something else. It\'s neither large nor small... it\'s somewhere in between, a round shape. Five are served in a portion, and its flavor will take you away. Since kebab shops don\'t get the best results when their ovens are cold, you should eat lahmacun in Adana at lunchtime or in the evening.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'lahmacun.avif', NULL, NULL, 0, 5, 8, 110, 173, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:55:38', '2026-04-30 07:55:39', NULL),
(244, NULL, NULL, 'Adana Kebab', NULL, 'adana-kebab', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>If you\'re going to eat Adana Kebab, whose fame extends beyond the city, you absolutely must choose it as a wrap. Only then can you experience that unique flavor where all the kebab\'s sauce is concentrated at the end of the wrap. If you want diced meat kebab, be sure to specify, because in Adana, if you order kebab, you\'ll get minced meat kebab. Your table is then adorned with complimentary side dishes such as tomatoes, green peppers, pickled ornamental peppers, watercress, mint, radishes, and sumac-flavored onion salad. All you have to do is enjoy this feast.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'adana-kebabi.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 5, 8, 111, 173, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:56:15', '2026-04-30 07:56:15', NULL),
(245, NULL, NULL, 'Places to See in Adana', NULL, 'places-to-see-in-adana', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Visitors participating in the International Orange Blossom Carnival have the opportunity to get to know Adana\'s historical and natural beauties up close. The Great Clock Tower, one of the city\'s landmarks; the Historic Stone Bridge, one of the oldest stone bridges in the world; the Sabancı Central Mosque, notable for its magnificent architecture; and the Seyhan River, which flows through the city, are among the main stops for those wishing to explore Adana\'s cultural and natural riches. Here are some places to see in Adana…</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'adanada-gorulmesi-gereken-yerler-icon-aazn.svg', NULL, 0, 27, 8, 113, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 07:57:18', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(246, NULL, NULL, 'Transportation to Adana', NULL, 'transportation-to-adana', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>There are direct flights to Çukurova International Airport from Istanbul Yeni, Istanbul Sabiha Gökçen, Ankara Esenboğa, İzmir Adnan Menderes, Lefkoşa Ercan, Antalya, Trabzon and Van airports. Adana can also be reached by bus and train.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'adanaya-ulasim-icon-wwdd.svg', NULL, 0, 1, 8, 115, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 08:05:02', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(247, NULL, NULL, 'Accommodation in Adana', NULL, 'accommodation-in-adana', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Adana stands out with its wide range of comfortable accommodation options, from five-star hotels to boutique choices. In addition to establishments boasting unique views of the Seyhan River, hotels located throughout the city welcome guests with high-quality service and a pleasant stay.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'adanada-konaklama-icon-weql.svg', NULL, 0, 28, 8, 114, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 08:05:52', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(249, NULL, NULL, 'Sustainability', NULL, 'sustainability', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The International Orange Blossom Carnival is more than just a cultural entertainment event; it has a sustainability vision encompassing economic, social, and environmental impacts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In many ways, it directly contributes to nine of the 17 United Nations Sustainable Development Goals and their sub-targets.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 9, 9, 13, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 08:08:36', '2026-04-30 12:16:01', NULL),
(250, NULL, NULL, 'Sustainability Podcasts', NULL, 'sustainability-podcasts', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The Orange Blossom Carnival Sustainability Podcast features in-depth conversations with experts on reducing the event\'s environmental impact, contributing to social responsibility projects, and achieving sustainability goals. Each episode shares the carnival\'s sustainability journey, innovative projects, and future plans with listeners.</p>\n\n                <p>Originnovation Podcast Episode: Carnival Sustainability Initiatives</p>\n\n                <p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/4vVZFvrb78OeYsGuPXO0CP?utm_source=generator\" style=\"border-radius:12px\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'surdurulebilirlik-podcastleri-ses-xkpv.mp3', NULL, 'surdurulebilirlik-podcastleri.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 9, 146, 249, 2, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 08:14:20', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(251, NULL, NULL, 'Sustainability Surveys', NULL, 'sustainability-surveys', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The results of the 2025 Carnival Participants Survey are now available.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe class=\"fp-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://heyzine.com/flip-book/c48dc42819.html\" style=\"border: 1px solid lightgray; width: 100%; height: 600px; margin-top: 25px\"></iframe></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'surdurulebilirlik-anketleri.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 9, 132, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 08:37:12', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(252, NULL, NULL, 'Sustainability Videos', NULL, 'sustainability-videos', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'surdurulebilirlik-videolari-xk41.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 30, 9, 131, 249, 2, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 08:37:42', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(253, NULL, NULL, 'Sustainability Reports', NULL, 'sustainability-reports', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The Orange Blossom Carnival, held in Adana every April, brings together thousands of participants with its colorful events. This report, prepared in line with the carnival\'s sustainability goals, details the progress made over the years in reducing the event\'s environmental impact, contributing to social responsibility projects, and increasing economic sustainability. By showcasing the carnival\'s achievements and future goals in the field of sustainability, this report highlights how the event contributes to a greener and more sustainable future.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'surdurulebilirlik-raporlari-4yhp.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 29, 9, 116, 249, 2, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 09:40:50', '2026-04-30 12:26:26', NULL),
(254, NULL, NULL, '2024 Sustainability Report', NULL, '2024-sustainability-report', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Türkiye\'s first event sustainability report has been published.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe class=\"fp-iframe enData\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://heyzine.com/flip-book/45272a77d3.html\" style=\"border: 1px solid lightgray; width: 100%; height: 500px;\"></iframe></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 9, 128, 253, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 09:43:31', '2026-04-30 09:44:11', NULL),
(255, NULL, NULL, 'Carnival Map', NULL, 'carnival-map', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>You can easily follow our events with the 2026 International Orange Blossom Carnival map.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe height=\"1000\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/1/embed?mid=1tcyjTOsXNVpFFlv6LLI3FAqILhHaDbY&amp;ehbc=2E312F\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 31, 10, NULL, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 09:45:57', '2026-04-30 09:45:57', NULL),
(256, NULL, NULL, '2026 Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı Geri Bildirim Anketi', NULL, '2026-portakal-cicegi-karnavali-geri-bildirim-anketi', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Portakal Çiçeği Karnavalı’nın ekonomik, toplumsal, kültürel ve deneyimsel etkisini bütüncül bir şekilde değerlendirmek amacıyla bu çalışma yürütülmektedir. Elde edilecek veriler; karnavalın şehir üzerindeki etkisini daha net ortaya koymak, katılımcı deneyimini anlamak ve gelecek yıllarda daha güçlü, daha sürdürülebilir ve daha etkili bir organizasyon kurgulamak için kullanılacaktır.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Çalışma kapsamında anketler, saha gözlemleri ve dijital veri analizleri birlikte değerlendirilerek kapsamlı bir etki analizi oluşturulmaktadır. Bu yaklaşım sayesinde yalnızca katılım ve memnuniyet değil, aynı zamanda davranışlar, harcama eğilimleri ve sürdürülebilirlik etkileri de analiz edilmektedir.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tüm veriler anonim olarak toplanmakta olup yalnızca etki analizi ve geliştirme amaçlı kullanılacaktır. Katkı sağlayan tüm katılımcılara teşekkür ederiz.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://forms.gle/JcBbu9jCiSLbuKok6\" style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(226, 131, 55); padding: 5px 0px; border-radius: 34px; margin-top: 20px; font-weight: 600;\" target=\"_blank\">Ankete ulaşmak için tıklayınız.</a></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-portakal-cicegi-karnavali-geri-bildirim-anketi-p4vo.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 2, NULL, 147, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 10:10:12', '2026-04-30 10:10:33', NULL),
(258, NULL, NULL, 'Announcements', NULL, 'announcements', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Visit our website to stay updated on the Orange Blossom Carnival\'s ever-expanding event calendar, prize-winning competitions, and other important announcements.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 32, 11, NULL, NULL, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 10:13:34', '2026-04-30 10:13:34', NULL),
(259, NULL, NULL, 'The dates for the International Orange Blossom Carnival have been announced.', NULL, 'the-dates-for-the-international-orange-blossom-carnival-have-been-announced', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The dates for the 14th International Orange Blossom Carnival, to be held in 2026, have been announced. The event, scheduled for April 1-5, 2026, is expected to attract hundreds of thousands of participants from both Turkey and abroad. The grand parade, part of the carnival which promises to be a cultural and artistic extravaganza, will take place on April 4, 2026.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'the-dates-for-the-international-orange-blossom-carnival-have-been-announced-bv8l.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 11, 151, 258, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 10:20:01', '2026-04-30 10:20:23', NULL),
(260, NULL, NULL, 'The carnival spirit is bringing life to nature this year too!', NULL, 'the-carnival-spirit-is-bringing-life-to-nature-this-year-too', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The International Orange Blossom Carnival is adding another initiative to its sustainability efforts by launching the Carnival Memorial Forest project.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This special memorial forest, to be created in two different areas of Adana in 2026, will both provide a breath of fresh air for the future and crown the carnival\'s love for nature.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>14th International Orange Blossom Carnival</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Get ready for this project that will breathe life into the future!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>April 1–5, 2026</strong></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'the-carnival-spirit-is-bringing-life-to-nature-this-year-too.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 11, 152, 258, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 10:21:17', '2026-04-30 10:21:17', NULL),
(261, NULL, NULL, 'The International Orange Blossom Carnival Memorial Forests have come to life!', NULL, 'the-international-orange-blossom-carnival-memorial-forests-have-come-to-life', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>We have given a breath of fresh air to the future with the two Carnival Memorial Forests established in the Çukurova and Karataş districts.<br />\r\nWe will continue to add value to nature and produce sustainable projects for a greener Adana.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe thank the Adana Forestry Directorate for their support in this meaningful work.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'the-international-orange-blossom-carnival-memorial-forests-have-come-to-life-o7uv.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 11, 155, 258, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 10:49:45', '2026-04-30 10:51:04', NULL),
(262, NULL, NULL, 'The excitement is even greater in Adana this April!', NULL, 'the-excitement-is-even-greater-in-adana-this-april', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The International Orange Blossom Carnival promises an unforgettable surprise for its visitors in 2026. HobbyPort Mediterranean Fair is included in the Carnival program as an associated event.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe energy of the Carnival transforms into a lifestyle festival with the HobbyPort Mediterranean Fair. Taking place in Adana from April 2-5, 2026, the HobbyPort Mediterranean Fair offers visitors the opportunity to discover their dream outdoor lifestyle and the latest hobby trends.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhile the Carnival represents fun, the streets, and togetherness, HobbyPort Mediterranean transforms this energy into personal passions and a desire to return to nature. The Carnival and HobbyPort create a synergy built on the philosophy of \"living life to the fullest.\" Visitors who will experience the carnival excitement in Adana amidst the scent of orange blossoms will also have the opportunity to discover their dream outdoor lifestyle and the latest hobby trends at the fairgrounds.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Why should Carnival visitors explore HobbyPort Mediterranean?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Complete Your Carnival Experience: Let the excitement of the streets continue with a passion for adventure! Crown the free spirit of the carnival with caravans, motorcycles, and outdoor equipment that will allow you to escape into nature.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDiscover the World of Hobbies: Not just for professionals; a wide range of inspiring content awaits visitors of all ages who want to make a fresh start, including caravans, tiny houses, hunting &amp; fishing, and outdoor sports.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSee the Lifestyle of the Future: From modular homes to eco-friendly solutions, experience firsthand the new lifestyle trends of modern man in harmony with nature.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWitness Regional Power: Be a firsthand witness to Adana becoming the largest hobby and outdoor trade center in the region.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Adventure Redefined in Adana in April!</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to the unforgettable parade and colorful events of the Orange Blossom Carnival, be sure to visit HobbyPort Mediterranean, where you\'ll find answers to your passions. This year, Adana is not just a carnival city; it\'s a meeting point for freedom, hobbies, and nature!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Date:</strong>&nbsp;April 2-5, 2026<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Location:</strong>&nbsp;Adana International Fair and Congress Center</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We invite all our carnival friends to experience this unique synergy firsthand and add a new color to their lives!</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'bu-yil-nisanda-adanada-cosku-daha-da-artiyor.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 11, 156, 258, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 11:12:23', '2026-04-30 11:12:25', NULL),
(263, NULL, NULL, 'Carnival Program is now available!', NULL, 'carnival-program-is-now-available', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<h2>The excitement of the 14th International Orange Blossom Carnival is about to begin!</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Between April 1st and 5th, Adana will host a packed program of events, from sporting activities and concerts to exhibitions and cultural and artistic performances. The colorful events, appealing to visitors of all ages from children to young people and women, will create unforgettable moments for guests from both within Turkey and abroad. You can view the detailed event program on our website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"medya/2026-portakal-cicegi-karnavali-programi.pdf\" style=\"font-size: 20px; line-height: 20px;  color:#e28337; padding: 5px 0; border-radius: 34px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 600;\">Click here to download the program.</a></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'karnaval-programi-yayinda-yfz3.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0, 33, 11, 157, 258, 2, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2026-04-30 11:17:49', '2026-04-30 11:17:49', NULL);
